Title : Fluffy Critter
Text : {{More citations needed|date=May 2014}}
A '''Fluffy Critter''' is a cocktail containing 2 shots of [[white rum]], [[Lime (fruit)|lime]] juice, [[lemonade]] and [[strawberry sauce]].<ref name="Bright" >{{cite news
| url= https://www.pressreader.com/usa/life-style-weekly/20171222/284378379684707
| title = Entertainment Reviews - Bright
| work = Pressreader.com
| date = 22 December 2017
| accessdate =5 May 2018
}}</ref>

This cocktail is easy to make and the contents can be altered according to taste.

